txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating the dreaded two-headed troll Stûg-and-Zar.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Ausma for your reward!

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].

'My scouts have come back having tracked a fearsome two-headed troll to its lair beneath a waterfall.

'Enter the caverns and put an end to the dreaded two-headed troll Stûg-and-Zar.'
The dreaded two-headed troll Stûg-and-Zar poses a grave threat to our cause.\n\nYour mission is to defeat this foul creature.
The monster commander in this mission will attempt a brutal wounding attack.
You have been tasked with defeating the dreaded two-headed troll Stûg-and-Zar.\n\nSpeak to Ausma to travel to seek out the creature.
'Well done! With the Stûg-and-Zar defeated, the foundation has been laid for our work in Gundabad!'
